title: Tues Post Show (10-11-22)
itunes:title: Tues Post Show (10-11-22)
description:
We start by giving behind the scenes of what happens during commercials breaks where we sing songs and try to figure them out. We talk about what’s going on inside our brains, looping thoughts and always having music in our heads. We try to teach Lunchbox how to sing. Bobby shares some of the difficulties he experiences with being left handed. We talk about the safest and least safest cities in America.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
